    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "### Problem\n\nCurrently, the builtin package manager does full clones by default. Would it be possible to expose shallow clone as an option in `vim.pack`?\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nPerhaps shallow by default, with full clone as an option.",
